<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cancellation Policy - Arknet Couriers</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gopher:wght@100&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Gopher', sans-serif;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 100;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #444;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <p>Cancellations can be made up to 24 hours before the pick-up time without any fee. No refunds will be given for deliveries that are cancelled less than 24 hours before the scheduled pick-up time.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
